name: HypnoSkull Serie 01
description:
1200x1200 px , base skull created using Alchemy, screentones, inksplashes and animations done in Photoshop.

This piece is my first ever animation, and the first of a serie of graphic exploration based on my skull design done with alchemy. It will be the first installment of a collection.

I explore various ways of creating appealing color schemes and new ways of creating loops over my drawings. 

Special thanks to Xponentialdesign for helping me planting the seeds.
